Lamborghini Considers Making a Third Model, FT Deutschland Says

-- B y   C h r i s t i a n   V i t s
-- 
2011-02-28T20:57:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-28/lamborghini-considers-making-a-third-model-ft-deutschland-says.html
Automobili Lamborghini SpA  is
considering adding a third model to its range and will make a
decision about it this year, Financial Times Deutschland
reported, citing an interview with Chief Executive Officer
Stephan Winkelmann. He said a new model could be launched by
2015 at the earliest, according to the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Christian Vits in Frankfurt at 
 cvits@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Craig Stirling at   cstirling1@bloomberg.net  